com.nimbusds.openid.connect.messages
Class AccessToken

java.lang.Object
  com.nimbusds.openid.connect.messages.AccessToken

public class AccessToken
extends java.lang.Object

OAuth 2.0 access token. Supports only bearer type tokens.

See draft-ietf-oauth-v2-26, section 1.4 and section 4.2.2.

Version:
0.9 (2012-05-17)
Author:
Vladimir Dzhuvinov
